{"tid":607200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（ 懷疑被戴帽 ）拍咗拖兩年 已經冇再 搞嘢","createTime":"2018-03-27T06:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T07:12:29.000Z","uid":99568,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9180e4985636e3f5ce403d2920c5c61fb58dd4","tid":607200,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:09:46.000Z","msg":"我同佢 拍咗拖兩年 <br />\n以前每個禮拜都至少做一次， 但係最近已經好耐冇同佢搞過<br />\n我開始好懷疑佢係咪俾帽我戴， 上個月我仲發現到佢偷偷地 玩ginder. <br />\n<br />\n但就係尋晚 佢突然話想著住校服比我搞 <br />\n<br />\n我 問佢去邊度買校服呀? <br />\n佢 就同我講著番我中學個套囉 <br />\n<br />\n佢係衣櫃拎左套校服出黎著左上身 <br />\n我即刻好似撻著左咁撲低左佢 <br />\n<br />\n我:一齊三年而家先知你讀英華<br />\n佢含情默默咁望住我<br />\n<br />\n就係咁 <br />\n我同佢 大戰咗三百回合， 今朝屙屎嗰屙 咗血， 唔知關唔關琴晚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗我同佢嘅關係又邁進咗一大步"},{"pid":"ae95f8085facce1aa4544fc9ccd47226f22a7cf8","tid":607200,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"後來我發現咗佢真係比帽我戴， 我捉住佢唔理佢點反抗都好， 我同佢講話 我唔會畀人背叛我， 然後我就 將我條巨龍吉咗入去， 最後 屌到佢流曬血 嗌唔好"},{"pid":"f8b03f8b15ca5f7e4d2daff78d6dbbb7479275bf","tid":607200,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de7125de6b30d53cca3292ed4a33c4b88551219","tid":607200,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b412dfa4bf79cb78cd1ce41c6d02e48e7f075b","tid":607200,"uid":147028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:13:16.000Z","msg":"Oh Shit !!!"},{"pid":"2871512645d5506e4610fe5591e2024f87c02963","tid":607200,"uid":91480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:13:22.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈"},{"pid":"97c5c2bd261c2b57ad457d1a1c2b08e432535093","tid":607200,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2871512645d5506e4610fe5591e20